post_text:
Football Updates from Coach Carter:

Player/coach meeting on Aug. 9th at 6pm at the Belfield football field.

Training camp starts Aug. 10th 6:30am to 8:30am, break from 8:30am to 9:30am, practice from 9:30am to 11am.

Football Gear checkout on Aug. 6th 10am to 2pm and 6pm to 8pm at Belfield school.

Gear check out Aug. 7th 10am to 2pm and 6pm to 8pm at Belfield school.

If players had their physical last year they do not need one this year. Please complete form B.

Go Cougars!
